      "Infectious period (1/gamma): 7.14 days\n",
      "This is used to convert case-days prevented -> approx unique cases prevented.\n",
      "\n",
      "Intervention                          Peak I   Peak Day   I at Day 120  Case-Days Prev  Cases Prev (approx)\n",
      "---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
      "No Intervention                       7047.0         87          834.6             0.0                  0.0\n",
      "Int 1: Masking                        3520.0         82         1105.2         80782.8              11309.6\n",
      "Int 2: Vaccine Campaign               6346.0         87          834.8         15928.9               2230.0\n",
      "Int 3: Vaccine Rollout                6507.7         87          701.9         19054.5               2667.6\n",
      "Int 4: Testing+Quarantine             2772.1         70            0.0        204941.0              28691.7\n",
      "Int 5: School Closure 2wks            4107.7        115         3949.1         82391.0              11534.7\n",
      "\n",
      "Note: 'Case-Days Prev' = area between I(t) curves; can exceed N.\n",
      "      'Cases Prev (approx)' = Case-Days Prev / 7.14 days; approx unique infections averted.\n"
     ]
